item.description: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_VirtualDedicatedRack Datatype Description SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_VirtualDedicatedRack models tracking objects specific to virtual dedicated racks. Bandwidth Pooling aggregate the bandwidth used by multiple servers within the rack. Local data The data recorded by a tracking object. Type: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Data[] id A tracking object's internal identifier. Type: integer label Tracking object label Type: string resourceTableId The identifier of the existing resource this object is attempting to track.
